{"tid":1309697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閩 粵 人 不 等 於 漢 人","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:21:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"32ac31f80ccca9f052de1b58e4c8e466996915cc","tid":1309697,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"&lt;轉貼PTT&gt;<br />\n閩粵人不等於漢人 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7ErazO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7ErazO5.jpg&h=89db5eeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3OKzY1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3OKzY1H.jpg&h=0521dc19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jkA3X71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjkA3X71.jpg&h=974e9ea3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n林媽利教授的馬偕團隊根據台灣人的血緣做出研究，發現多數&quot;台灣人&quot;其實是平埔族與閩 粵移民的混血，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而閩粵移民其實是漢化的越人，並非我們一直以為的&quot;中原漢人&quot;。</span></span> 這套說法並沒有寫入教科書中，所以多數人仍以為，閩粵移民也是漢人，所以也應該是中 國人，而不知道，閩粵人其實早就拋棄了自己的越人文化，被漢文化同化。 可悲的是，平埔人也以為自己是漢人，然後高山族以為漢化的平埔是閩人，然後一併厭惡 之。這就表現在高山原民寧願把票給國民黨，而不願給本土、操閩南語(=漢化平埔)的民 進黨。 在這樣的基礎上，台灣的母語運動追尋的是誰的母語？台灣人使用的漢語文應該怎樣定位 ，都是個值得深思的問題。 但台灣人絕對不是純粹的漢人。而台灣人是不是中國人，就要看你覺得中國人的定義是什 麼了。 補~ 想深入了解就自己去翻這本書，我整理的內容有限，文本就在那裡，請自行檢視運用。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UfYf1WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUfYf1WY.jpg&h=5c42f1eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qSnQ38H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqSnQ38H.jpg&h=c40276fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbstop.amassly.com%2Fpost%2FGossiping_1LH8CpVu&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUym2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=aa3ef6c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbstop.amassly.com/post/Gossiping_1LH8CpVu</a>"},{"pid":"93fa8438414aafe250f465973234113d0d74f7d1","tid":1309697,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b71a657f5c31751c5197a7aa98b5faf466d8ef","tid":1309697,"uid":115096,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"用血統基因去講漢人真係白痴<br />\n漢族其實係繼承秦國<br />\n秦國將中原以至南越各種族炒埋一碟<br />\n所以漢族係多種族多基因社群<br />\n即係美國人係乜血統基因呢？<br />\n黑白黃紅全部都有呀"},{"pid":"1dfcac82b0b41b4ad8b5c9fa2b0929deafbc51dd","tid":1309697,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"魏晉南北朝300年間<br />\n中原人被殺得7788<br />\n大批胡人入侵<br />\n中原文化血統大雜燴"},{"pid":"fef609f53e83b6fe32fb32189f926cbd7ec9ae1a","tid":1309697,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73108a4246a43c25cc0d42aed4b1d4fe019463ed","tid":1309697,"uid":23162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"全部南蠻嚟唔同語唔同種，唔係自己人"},{"pid":"374e7d1c471290942df1007dd28800c0fbb688c6","tid":1309697,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"閩粵人被屈做南漢人<br />\n鄭成功父係福建人 母係日本人<br />\n歷史書稱鄭成功做漢人<br />\n中原漢人曾幾何時統治過台灣？<br />\n閩粵自秦漢被中原人侵殖<br />\n已經統治千多年！"},{"pid":"a1a6f15b7fa2bb1d2294317faea5ca2caa204d62","tid":1309697,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"種族主義話同自己差唔多樣,講同一個語言既就係人類<br />\n民族主義純粹係文化概念,同血統冇絕對關係<br />\n唔通香港人同廣東人係自己人咩<br />\n而且又唔係全部香港人都係廣東黎既"},{"pid":"3b6a0bb9796ba6a677e8858c41daef69b2a4f672","tid":1309697,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1a6f15b7fa2bb1d2294317faea5ca2caa204d62","tid":1309697,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:44:04.000Z","msg":